          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1598435079541-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, rinse the <strong>quinoa</strong> in a sieve under cold running water</p><p>Add the <strong>quinoa </strong>to a pot with a matching lid with 180ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[360ml]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for an initial 10-12 min</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1598435090898-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1598435090898-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1598435090898-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
