            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, roughly chop the <strong>basil</strong>, including the stalks</p><p>Peel and roughly chop the<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> chopped basil </strong>and<strong> garlic</strong> to the <strong>pestle and mortar </strong>with the <strong>remaining walnuts </strong>and grind to a paste – this is your <strong>walnut pesto</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
