    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain and rinse the<strong> butter beans </strong>and wash the<strong> spinach</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>drained butter beans </strong>and <strong>washed spinach</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until the spinach has started to wilt</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
